Product - Perpetual





































 











Skip to content








Perpetual
making a material difference

















Product 




Yarns










Products










Brands










Yarns














We manufacture 100% sustainable yarns that offer sustainable comfort performance and protection.  Our range includes textured filament yarns from 50-1200 deniers. Our yarns is supplied for use in various applications, circular knitting , warp knitting, seamless knitting, weaving, mesh, fleece, denim and many other applications in the apparel work-wear, automotive, furnishings and technical textiles. Our R&D team is continuously challenging themselves to develop new specialized yarns to suit the dynamic needs of our customers, some examples of these efforts include recycled yarns with moisture management -torque yarns,  capabilities, fully drawn yarns, (FDY), de torque yarns, recycled yarns with lycra and spandex. We also offer partially oriented yarns (POY) to select partners for further specialised applications.





Products









Over the last decade, the global consumption of polyester has grown. The apparel and home textile segments account for more than 79% of the total fibre consumption. Polyester is the fabric of choice for sports-wear where its ability to “wick” away sweat is highly beneficial. Polyester is also much more durable than cotton and its elastic nature is used widely within a range of textile products including bags, denims and furnishings. Our yarns are used in thousands of products worldwide.





Brands














Perpetual  recycled yarn is used by some of the worlds well-known brands. We have joined partnerships with brands, mills and various organisations to reduce the impact we have on the environment. We offer transparency and tracebility in our supply chain.























































































































































































