News & insights from Perpetual













Information on IMPACT Philanthropy

























NOT MUCH HAS CHANGED. BUT EVERYTHING HAS CHANGED.


From Decimal to Digital: Lessons from 50 years of investing in Australian shares. This book is not all about the Perpetual Industrial Share Fund – though it celebrates 50 years of that fund. It’s about the country the fund invests in, how it’s changed and why.                                 


Download your copy




















WHY IT PAYS TO NEVER FALL IN LOVE


Detachment, focus and logic. Not exactly attributes that evoke excitement, yet at Perpetual they’re exactly what we apply to every decision we make across our wide range of investments. Here’s what our investment managers do to minimise downside risk and grow clients’ wealth.                                


Find out more




















IMPACT PHILANTHROPY AND NFP INSIGHTS


IMPACT provides insight into important issues for philanthropists and the not-for-profit sector. It shares thought provoking ideas and best practice examples that aim to both stimulate and motivate a passion for philanthropy with Impact.                                


Read the latest issue of IMPACT




















GLOBAL INVESTORS EYE AUSTRALIA


A recent study conducted by Perpetual has found Australian RMBS is in demand among global investors, but Australia is not capitalising on the extent of opportunity.                                


Find out more




















